snippet.title: SM64 The Green Stars - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Version 1.3 of the hack is now released (as of 31st August 2013)!!! Download if you haven't already :3


Pre-Patched Download: http://www.mediafire.com/?vyvb6dj5jthbicv
Patch Download (Only download if you know how to patch): http://www.mediafire.com/?bf99fuxblekxx9w

Hello Youtube! My SM64 hack has been released! After over 2 years of me working on it, I have finally completed it :D

Over the 2 years I have gone through many problems, I've been unmotivated and lazy with it as well. It has only been recently that I have had the desire to get it done and here it is for you guys!
If you find any bugs or things in the game, just let me know. If it's something major then I'll have to fix it. Anyway, enjoy the video, and if you download, enjoy the game!

Music:
F-777 Yin and Yang

10000 views achieved 17th February 2015!
